View

Class AbstractFileWindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.stage.Window
      • javafx.stage.Stage
        • View.AbstractFileWindow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.event.EventTarget
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OpenFileWindow, SaveFileWindow

    abstract class AbstractFileWindow
extends javafx.stage.Stage
    Abstract class for Open and Save file window This class make stage with parameter ( title and controller file ) It is designed by FileWindow.fxml file in /View/Fxml package It has two label, two text area, two button for open or left and right file Created by woojin on 2016-05-18.
    Author:
    woojin Jang
